## Directory-based project format:
# Track shared IntelliJ configurations but ignore user-specific files
.idea/workspace.xml
.idea/tasks.xml
.idea/dictionaries/
.idea/shelf/
.idea/usage.statistics.xml
.idea/inspectionProfiles/profiles_settings.xml

# Sensitive or high-churn files (ignore):
.idea/dataSources.ids
.idea/sqlDataSources.xml
.idea/dynamic.xml

# Keep shared configurations (track these):
# .idea/runConfigurations/ - Keep for shared run configs
# .idea/codeStyles/ - Keep for shared code style
# .idea/liveTemplates/ - Keep for shared templates
# .idea/dataSources.xml - Keep for shared database connections
# .idea/gradle.xml - Keep for shared Gradle settings
# .idea/kubernetes.xml - Keep for shared K8s settings
# .idea/docker-compose.xml - Keep for shared Docker settings

